<br>
That's just my take on things...a successful guild has selective membership, to weed out the folks that don't fit in with the rest.  I've seen too many guilds break apart due to poor membership decisions that led to reputation issues and general mayhem, and that is always an ugly thing.<br>
<br>
Just my take on things, and I've had some rum this eve, so I apologize if there is a garbled train of thought.  Have a good eve!<br>
<br>
